# This is where we keep a hacked oUF core.
#
# oUF is maintained for WoW Retail only. However, the ElvUI team maintains a
# fork, which works on any version and can be dropped here.
#
# ElvUI's oUF contains compatibility code and may be slightly inefficient for
# us, because we only aim to support one WoW version.
#
# Patching oUF is do-able, but tedious. We stick with ElvUI's oUF core for now.
# I will not *distribute* that one, though. Let's honor the work they put into
# that awesome UI!
